colubrisAAAClientMIB.name: colubrisAAAClientMIB
colubrisAAAClientMIB.contactinfo: Colubris Networks Postal: 200 West Street Ste 300 Waltham, Massachusetts 02451-1121 UNITED STATES Phone: +1 781 684 0001 Fax: +1 781 684 0009 E-mail: cn-snmp@colubris.com
colubrisAAAClientMIB.description: Colubris Networks AAA Client MIB file.

colubrisAAAProfileTable.name: colubrisAAAProfileTable
colubrisAAAProfileTable.description: A table defining the AAA server profiles currently configured on the device.

colubrisAAAProfileEntry.name: colubrisAAAProfileEntry
colubrisAAAProfileEntry.description: A AAA server profile configured in the device. colubrisAAAProfileIndex - Uniquely identifies the profile within the profile table.

colubrisAAAProfileIndex.name: colubrisAAAProfileIndex
colubrisAAAProfileIndex.description: Specifies the index of the AAA server profile.

colubrisAAAProfileName.name: colubrisAAAProfileName
colubrisAAAProfileName.description: Specifies the name of the AAA server profile.

colubrisAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex.name: colubrisAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex
colubrisAAAProfilePrimaryServerIndex.description: Indicates the index number of the primary server profile in the table. A value of zero indicates that no AAA server is defined.

colubrisAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex.name: colubrisAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex
colubrisAAAProfileSecondaryServerIndex.description: Indicates the index number of the secondary server profile in the table. A value of zero indicates that no AAA server is defined.

colubrisAAAServerTable.name: colubrisAAAServerTable
colubrisAAAServerTable.description: A table containing the AAA servers currently configured on the device.

colubrisAAAServerEntry.name: colubrisAAAServerEntry
colubrisAAAServerEntry.description: An AAA server configured on the device. colubrisAAAServerIndex - Uniquely identifies a server inside the server table.

colubrisAAAServerIndex.name: colubrisAAAServerIndex
colubrisAAAServerIndex.description: Specifies the index of the AAA server in the table.

colubrisAAAAuthenProtocol.name: colubrisAAAAuthenProtocol
colubrisAAAAuthenProtocol.description: Indicates the protocol used by the AAA client to communicate with the AAA server.

colubrisAAAAuthenMethod.name: colubrisAAAAuthenMethod
colubrisAAAAuthenMethod.description: Indicates the authentication method used by the AAA client to authenticate users via the AAA server.

colubrisAAAServerName.name: colubrisAAAServerName
colubrisAAAServerName.description: Specifies the IP address of the AAA server. The string must be a valid IP address in the format 'nnn.nnn.nnn.nnn' Where 'nnn' is a number in the range [0..255]. The '.' character is mandatory between the fields.

colubrisAAASharedSecret.name: colubrisAAASharedSecret
colubrisAAASharedSecret.description: Specifies the shared secret used by the AAA client and the AAA server. This attribute should only be set if AAA traffic between the AAA client and server is sent through a VPN tunnel. Reading this attribute will always return a zero-length string.

colubrisAAAAuthenticationPort.name: colubrisAAAAuthenticationPort
colubrisAAAAuthenticationPort.description: Indicates the port number used by the AAA client to send authentication requests to the AAA server.

colubrisAAAAccountingPort.name: colubrisAAAAccountingPort
colubrisAAAAccountingPort.description: Indicates the port number used by the AAA client to send accounting information to the AAA server.

colubrisAAATimeout.name: colubrisAAATimeout
colubrisAAATimeout.description: Indicates how long the AAA client will wait for an answer to an authentication request.

colubrisAAANASId.name: colubrisAAANASId
colubrisAAANASId.description: Indicates the network access server ID to be sent by the AAA client in each authentication request sent to the AAA server.

colubrisAAAClientMIBCompliance.name: colubrisAAAClientMIBCompliance
colubrisAAAClientMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the Colubris Networks AAA client MIB.

colubrisAAAProfileMIBGroup.name: colubrisAAAProfileMIBGroup
colubrisAAAProfileMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the AAA profile capability.

colubrisAAAClientMIBGroup.name: colubrisAAAClientMIBGroup
colubrisAAAClientMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing the AAA client MIB capability.
